# DNS provider modules compiled into Caddy AND Matcad's import binary.
# Add more from https://github.com/caddy-dns (space-separated) and rebuild:
#   ./scripts/deploy.ps1
# Any compiled-in module can then be used via the "Custom" provider type in the UI.
CADDY_DNS_MODULES=github.com/caddy-dns/netcup github.com/caddy-dns/cloudflare github.com/caddy-dns/digitalocean github.com/caddy-dns/hetzner github.com/caddy-dns/route53 github.com/caddy-dns/gandi github.com/caddy-dns/desec github.com/caddy-dns/ovh
